-- China Expands Xiamen Economic Zone to Entire City, Securities News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-20T23:07:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-20/china-expands-xiamen-economic-zone-to-entire-city-securities-news-reports.html

          
          
             China has approved expansion of a
special economic zone in Xiamen to cover the entire coastal city
in Fujian province, the Shanghai Securities News reported today,
citing Sun Chunlan, Communist Party secretary of the province.
The State Council has also approved the formation of a cross-
strait regional financial service center in Xiamen, the
Shanghai-based newspaper reported.  
